e="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;">为了积极配合国内对ESG人才的需求，<strong style="outline: 0px;">中国工商联人才交流服务中心和中国科技金融促进会于去年正式推出了国内的ESG证书，也是中文版的ESG证书，即</strong></span><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(40, 169, 167);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;">注册ESG分析师</strong></span><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;">。</strong></span></span><o:p style="outline: 0px;"></o:p></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 0.5em;padding-left: 0.5em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100002769" data-ratio="0.49074074074074076" data-type="png" data-w="1080" height="296.76724409448815px" style="outline: 0px;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0em 0em 0.5em 0px;width: 486px !important;visibility: visible !important;" width="604.7333333333333" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/EM73hF17Kziaya0c23qfoH3KjuQnIOqLOwricjicK5mzmBeIiaY5XmNMlEGSwichMKW1M4ibcntEaxvibAiaQ8zbgQicMPg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=wxpic&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"><o:p style="outline: 0px;"></o:p></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 0.5em;padding-left: 0.5em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-align: justify;"></span><br></p><p style="margin: 3pt 0pt;outline: 0px;font-family: 等线;font-size: 10.5pt;line-height: 18.2px;"><span style="outline: 0px;white-space-collapse: prese